{"tid":2465961,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人有睇魔都精兵的奴隸－賣肉打怪漫畫","createTime":"2021-03-28T17:22:21.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-17T05:35:57.000Z","uid":179956,"like":13,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"b9e085780df23d5ad9b6904fa79bed3df38c6c72","tid":2465961,"uid":179956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-28T17:22:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmXiwWX99NfrrLQHLDiBzPkC34C7N6u5seXijWykRVdxws?filename=JySwZoD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJySwZoD.jpg&h=e796b4b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n官方PV<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3G3HBFr5FkY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D3G3HBFr5FkY&d=BSPHu9UqRwj8n7oVkU4q%2BbTKTGNgLIIXgyzGYx6bzTs%3D&h=2e855db4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3G3HBFr5FkY</a><br />\n<blockquote>日本各地出現了異空間「魔都」──由於只有女性能從魔都的「桃」得到特異的能力，因此便由女兵組成了「魔防隊」。某一天，過著抑鬱生活的男高中生──和倉優希不小心闖進了突發性產生的魔都入口，在那裡，遇到了「魔防隊」第七組的美麗隊長──羽前京香，而她竟向優希宣言：「我要你當我的奴隸。」</blockquote><br />\n不過呢套劇情唔重要 最緊要係d女畫得正 同埋為咗滿足奴隸(觀眾)慾望 有唔同嘅play<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n錫不同地方 用口餵糖 腳play<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 尺度應該係同to love 差唔多<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過啲人設好似係參考得太多<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQgQ7sQbvmuoyErFDpyuiGYhy7iDAgr4kAJCpurRcNjdD?filename=x6WNxKV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx6WNxKV.png&h=b04400da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一花<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZs5Td9MEnneEeKK1Yf9iP1ztRZNRXwUDa6EDaYRkNEUv?filename=EhrJQyq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEhrJQyq.jpg&h=52ee7381&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n四葉 連諸葛四葉都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVWmgDHrEd4w6SDwnTJt3tKg2FNQBdcSKhM8UYsEDkUeR?filename=mds81Hd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fmds81Hd.png&h=aae9ec79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmRfQMAMRNcxg2YdSKi3aqdQfUFMwmnb3GrS9qCHnDFs2g?filename=cFZGCeD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcFZGCeD.png&h=2266521c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n女主就有啲似02"},{"pid":"4ab656d5eef461aed2582c7fff57313a100fc5d6","tid":2465961,"uid":75050,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-28T17:32:17.000Z","msg":"睇左，後面九成有ntr <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1b1f2ee80303508953875945736b3e75c751d30","tid":2465961,"uid":179956,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4ab656d5eef461aed2582c7fff57313a100fc5d6","tid":2465961,"uid":75050,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-28T17:32:17.000Z","msg":"睇左，後面九成有ntr <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-28T17:43:18.000Z","msg":"而家都係咁share用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我覺得係後宮方向"},{"pid":"918cd595262a9008e617e368e1073a93a2ee2eec","tid":2465961,"uid":102872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-03-28T18:07:01.000Z","msg":"斬赤個作者受咗咩刺激<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n平行天堂個作者又係，180度轉型<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"473d61bba6a3a979f64f51d95a605abfda284815","tid":2465961,"uid":2889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-28T18:17:28.000Z","msg":"有冇扑野場面"},{"pid":"2a67fe4f09abedb9671201f309a2222a144cbcc0","tid":2465961,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-28T18:19:59.000Z"